	Releasing 0.9.34. -CG

Thu Feb 20 14:17:05 CET 2014
	W32: Added creation of libmicrohttpd.lib, libmicrohttpd.def,
	libmicrohttpd.exp and libmicrohttpd-static.lib for easy use
	compiled MHD with MSVC.
