	POLL. -CG

Wed Mar 23 23:24:25 CET 2011
	Do not use POLLIN when we only care about POLLHUP (significantly
	improves performance when using MHD_USE_THREAD_PER_CONNECTION
	in combination with MHD_USE_POLL). -ES

